Package: connectcore
Title: Reusable Base for REST and WebSocket Data-Source Connectors
Version: 0.0.0.9000
URL: https://dereckscompany.github.io/connectcore,
    https://github.com/dereckscompany/connectcore
BugReports: https://github.com/dereckscompany/connectcore/issues
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Dereck",
           family = "Mezquita",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dereck@mezquita.io",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9307-6762"))
Description: Shared transport base for R data-source connectors: a configurable REST client (httr2; sync/async; retry; pluggable signing and error handling; pagination) and an event-driven WebSocket client (auto-reconnect, keepalive, watchdog, extensible dispatch). Connector packages extend it instead of re-implementing transport.
